Watch any 3 Episodes of your choice for free by creating an FYI Profile. Just look for the Get 3 Free Episodes prompt at launch or on any locked video. Hey FYI fans! We made some big updates for you: Watch your favorite FYI Shows on the big screen with Google Cast! Binge you favorite Show without having to lift a finger we ll queue up the next video for you! Use your TV Provider account to sign into ALL you Apps with Apple s TV Provider feature Easily get back to your favorite Show with Search History We want to hear what you think! Please reach out to us at FYIAppResearch aenetworks.com with any questions or comments!

Hey FYI fans! Enjoy all your favorite FYI shows in a whole new way! We ve made some major updates to the App that we hope you ll love. With this new version of the App you can now: Easily Browse or Search for your shows Quickly jump to any Season Watch video in Portrait or Landscape Keep track of what you ve watched We d love to hear what you think! Please send your comments to fyiappresearch aenetworks.com

Hey FYI Fans! Now you can start an episode on the Web during lunch and continue watching on your iPhone or iPad when you get home. Just create a quick profile and we ll do the rest that is we ll remember your place and we won t force you watch the ads again. We also fixed some bugs along the way. Let us know how it works: watchapps aenetworks.com
